Sure, here are some example sentences that use the word "celi" in different forms and positions:

1. *Celi* dan sam proveo u gradu. (I spent the *whole* day in the city.)
2. *Cela* zgrada je bila zatvorena zbog renoviranja. (The *entire* building was closed due to renovation.)
3. Upravo sam *celu* knjigu pročitao za jedno popodne. (I just read the *whole* book in one afternoon.)
4. *Cele* nedelje sam se pripremao za ispit. (I studied for the *entire* week for the exam.)
5. Želim da mi *celi* svet čuje glas. (I want my voice to be heard *all over* the world.)
6. Na kraju smo *celi* stigli do cilja. (In the end, we *all* made it to the finish line.)
7. *Celoj* porodici sam pripremio ručak. (I made lunch for the *whole* family.)
8. Sutra planiram da provedem *ceo* dan na plaži. (Tomorrow, I plan to spend the *entire* day at the beach.)

I hope these examples are helpful!